Name: libpepper_tokens
Summary: C/C++ Pepper Library (tokens)
License: MIT

BuildRequires: gcc
BuildRequires: gcc-c++
BuildRequires: make
BuildRequires: cmake
BuildRequires: libext_gtest
BuildRequires: libext_boost

>> Description
C/C++ In-house Library [Pepper] - Tokens
>>

>> Build
cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=${RPM_BUILD_ROOT}/usr .
make
make test
>>

>> Install
make install
>>

>> Clean
rm -rf ${RPM_BUILD_ROOT}
>>

>> Files
%defattr(-,root,root,-)
/usr/lib/libpepper-tokens.a
